{"tid":1764933,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗今日又發癲 但其實咁先有光明出路","createTime":"2019-12-01T12:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T15:41:45.000Z","uid":130797,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"acf9cf0cee53b0df2e1326b8b83d28e3b37f2537","tid":1764933,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"同老母今日出去行左轉<br />\n突然食左少少煙 老母興過火屎係咁屌鳩班狗亂咁黎無人性<br />\n<br />\n但其實諗深一層<br />\n人權法又過左 其他國家亦都開始想跟隊<br />\n而家見到班狗又亂咬人<br />\n最頭痕一定係上層做決策個班狗官<br />\n因為法案過左 下一步就梗係希望個report好睇<br />\n咁個report係以咩程度黎做評估?<br />\n我地諗返法案加速過個陣發生咩事 &gt; 中理大被圍攻<br />\n至少手足既反擊係完全被美帝接收納<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好喇 咁即係除左有不反同無不反既遊行之外<br />\n即使有手足出下火魔 係充分原因之下裝修<br />\n班狗只要任何武力回應市民發聲 <br />\n都有幾會變成人權狀況不達標不理想<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我簡單d講<br />\n即係只要唯持住我地一貫既遊行 (有無不反都無所謂)<br />\n和理非又好 勇武都好 繼續keep住每星期行動<br />\n只要班狗繼續用咁既方式去回應市民<br />\n咁港共 甚至係中共都一定唔可以就手旁觀<br />\n行動只有兩個大原則<br />\n1. 盡量小心不被捕不受傷 亦都盡量唔好一個人落單<br />\n2. 保持人數 質量 同埋持久打長期戰<br />\n<br />\n天佑我城<br />\n光復香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047ea320142307f1039de4f904f3f70df6c9776e","tid":1764933,"uid":321050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位promote下。香港人贏唔贏靠尼個：<br />\n<br />\n非建制區議員平台<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1764928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1764928</a>"},{"pid":"28ee0c9b49024ba7edeec946655255eecd0b283a","tid":1764933,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"始終會拉哂拉到冇人再岀"},{"pid":"c53d9cd11bf95ac932f91956a46e53d110fefc8c","tid":1764933,"uid":130797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"28ee0c9b49024ba7edeec946655255eecd0b283a","tid":1764933,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"始終會拉哂拉到冇人再岀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:04:53.000Z","msg":"如果班狗真係暴力濫捕升級到無人再敢出街<br />\n我相信只會係增加狗官壓力<br />\n<br />\n偏向打國際線<br />\n只係因為我地岩打國際線<br />\n廣東大媽勇猛車煙花<br />\n可惜過左幾個月我地都明白香港人根本唔係勇武既料<br />\n(我唔係話勇武手足弱 而係實際上和理非升級太慢太有底線)<br />\n<br />\n結果都係由懲罰班狗既老闆<br />\n再由佢地老闆去懲罰佢地先係一個比較可行既方向<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882a51c9dc8d8bddd94713073bbf17f86df1d1e9","tid":1764933,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"唔係戰術po<br />\n推兩野就算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723c49f345446e619f1d39d7703996ad55c11da7","tid":1764933,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a376fb4f2b1ce3d6d378a676681e8961b11aa205","tid":1764933,"uid":22796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"不嬲班綠曱甴都唔撚驚其他國家制裁乜乜柒柒<br />\n如果真係驚一早就收晒火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係班狗官嚇到瀨屎係咁屌老美啫<br />\nBTW班狗官點都唔敢屌綠曱甴<br />\n因為佢哋有武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabac8a3d784d7de587e69cae4060c904dbaf2e0","tid":1764933,"uid":340189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:20:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">堅持就會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b24a67c0c6dc806982f529ffbafa9d36dca7b83e","tid":1764933,"uid":116074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28ee0c9b49024ba7edeec946655255eecd0b283a","tid":1764933,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"始終會拉哂拉到冇人再岀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:21:51.000Z","msg":"其實大家都知對家濫捕 <br />\n<br />\n呢個係佢地犯錯，亦係我地不滿既位 <br />\n<br />\n當然會有人怕，但係諗深一層，怕，一開始唔應該出黎，即使我地係和理非。<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動就係克服恐懼既運動，睇下自己去到邊啲位啫<br />\n<br />\np.s. UA保釋緊"},{"pid":"400b803854a5149cee0c1ddecba2c9252291325f","tid":1764933,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1879f647917ad9d87b2cc75bd60e259178cf19","tid":1764933,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a376fb4f2b1ce3d6d378a676681e8961b11aa205","tid":1764933,"uid":22796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"不嬲班綠曱甴都唔撚驚其他國家制裁乜乜柒柒<br />\n如果真係驚一早就收晒火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係班狗官嚇到瀨屎係咁屌老美啫<br />\nBTW班狗官點都唔敢屌綠曱甴<br />\n因為佢哋有武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"講到錢銀野<br />\n實有d收成期緊既傻佬會表示不滿既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cab62bcc5770bd053d1d1f98324563636cdc43","tid":1764933,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de1879f647917ad9d87b2cc75bd60e259178cf19","tid":1764933,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a376fb4f2b1ce3d6d378a676681e8961b11aa205","tid":1764933,"uid":22796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"不嬲班綠曱甴都唔撚驚其他國家制裁乜乜柒柒<br />\n如果真係驚一早就收晒火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係班狗官嚇到瀨屎係咁屌老美啫<br />\nBTW班狗官點都唔敢屌綠曱甴<br />\n因為佢哋有武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"講到錢銀野<br />\n實有d收成期緊既傻佬會表示不滿既<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl