<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"記得有個巴打提過<br />\n軍政府其實係指緊確實真係由軍人執政既政權<br />\n但實際香港呢班傻仔只係地區散仔<br />\n即係隨時隨地都會一夜變condom呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adc67e9070f90bcb8bbe1a976b409ad87948f2e","tid":1764933,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ae434091428fd5c4eb7646573508bedd15b221f","tid":1764933,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f154a3ab46827ab88ed6a17e9b076c62c987e66b","tid":1764933,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a376fb4f2b1ce3d6d378a676681e8961b11aa205","tid":1764933,"uid":22796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"不嬲班綠曱甴都唔撚驚其他國家制裁乜乜柒柒<br />\n如果真係驚一早就收晒火啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係班狗官嚇到瀨屎係咁屌老美啫<br />\nBTW班狗官點都唔敢屌綠曱甴<br />\n因為佢哋有武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T13:54:50.000Z","msg":"軍政府係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"記得有個巴打提過<br />\n軍政府其實係指緊確實真係由軍人執政既政權<br />\n但實際香港呢班傻仔只係地區散仔<br />\n即係隨時隨地都會一夜變condom呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"泰國咪就係咁<br />\n香港軍政府只係中共撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca01d66327bd621c8bdae1dcce21954107f4078","tid":1764933,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"唔係戰術po<br />\n推埋呢野就算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c660dd2447cabda3f911b4915e0aae428cfc3de","tid":1764933,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:19:32.000Z","msg":"不受傷<br />\n不被捕<br />\n不流血<br />\n<br />\n講易行難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d8ae16ccd68fc92dc19248e5af0e895deec065","tid":1764933,"uid":130797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c660dd2447cabda3f911b4915e0aae428cfc3de","tid":1764933,"uid":63029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:19:32.000Z","msg":"不受傷<br />\n不被捕<br />\n不流血<br />\n<br />\n講易行難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"行動大原則黎<br />\n今時今日我話想大家全身而退 我都會覺得自己天真<br />\n但如果可以係大家心入面種落左個概念<br />\n就只望大家會放眼去持久出席活動<br />\n而唔會下下都end game咁去搵命相搏<br />\n<br />\n當然我地都可以打網路抗爭一年<br />\n再等美帝寫報告話香港人權不合格<br />\n不過我相信有班狗既失控畫面 <br />\n就更加易做到國會上下一致通過<br />\n班狗官係呢一年既心理壓力更大更早爆煲更早飛起班狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2386d94b06a5e5575d72e5fbbfadaa27ddbc15","tid":1764933,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54c878b0c5e61b16df19dd4e45787073afd1bab2","tid":1764933,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"［廣告界不是condom] 推2號開始黎明行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1764022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1764022</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedc57174ce3fe57c1fe69ea1d080bc7ad73d405","tid":1764933,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"愈亂愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f06514fceb3b4490f9251ebc2de5c894e688c2","tid":1764933,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:30:38.000Z","msg":"Any肥<br />\n大家記得事無大小都要推俾美帝議員做備案呀<br />\n報告咁長幫佢地做好個database都係我地既責任<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e148e85479c5e896f72beb7954a57ae35072f9f2","tid":1764933,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"其實班狗根本就唔想件事完<br />\n<br />\n佢地個個月袋緊10皮人工<br />\n<br />\n已經玩左半年 玩多半年個個散仔都儲到成球野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}